Gold is a mineral used by the banks to backup the currency. It is extracted (and perhaps smelted, who can tell?)  in the [[Main/en/Gold Mine]] and stored or coined in the [[Main/en/Bank]].

Gold can only be found in the [[Main/en/Climate#Sub-arctic|Sub-artic climate]].